data.description: Gorgeous and Renovated 3/2 Home + Bonus Room in Garage , build in 2001 in half acres lot. The roof was replaced in 2018.Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer are Brand New, Inside AC machine is literally 6 months old. Spacious tile thru the entire home with 2006 square footage under air conditioner, plus the bonus room build in the garage with tile and a split AC in place . When you come into the home, you will find an open floor concept with a beautiful gray kitchen and spacious island with a sink in the middle. The master bedroom is a nice size with a walk-in closet, Master bathroom and Guest bath has been remodeled with a large walk in shower and beautiful Frameless shower doors. Guest rooms are in the other side away from master room. Nice screened lenai plus a huge concrete flooring on the side of it that is in the backyard area. SOLAR PANEL FREE,FOR DETAILS PLEASE READ CONFIDENTIAL REMARKS... Dont wait any longer!!!! Come and see this beautiful home, make your Appt to see it today... It's ready to move in!!!
